        {
            "id": "835120509",
            "title": "1月14日热门中概股多数下跌 阿里巴巴涨0.40%，拼多多跌5.40%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article\" id=\"artibody\">\n<!-- 相关专题top start-->\n<!-- 相关专题top end-->\n<!-- 期货推广begin -->\n<!-- 期货推广end -->\n<!-- 秒拍begin -->\n<!-- 秒拍end -->\n<!-- 视频播放器start -->\n<!-- 视频播放器end -->\n<!-- 行情图begin -->\n<!-- 行情图end -->\n<p>　　1月14日热门中概股多数下跌，<span id=\"usstock_.IXIC\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/.IXIC.html\" target=\"_blank\">纳斯达克</a></span><span id=\"quote_.IXIC\"></span>中国金龙指数（HXC）收跌1.86%。</p>\n<p>　　上涨股当中（按市值从高到低），<span id=\"usstock_BABA\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/BABA.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span id=\"usstock_BABA\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/BABA.html\" target=\"_blank\">阿里</a></span><span id=\"quote_BABA\"></span>巴巴</a></span><span id=\"quote_BABA\"></span>涨0.40%，<span id=\"usstock_ASX\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/ASX.html\" target=\"_blank\">日月光半导体</a></span><span id=\"quote_ASX\"></span>涨2.38%，<span id=\"usstock_ZTO\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/ZTO.html\" target=\"_blank\">中通</a></span><span id=\"quote_ZTO\"></span>涨0.14%。</p>\n<p>　　下跌股当中（按市值从高到低），<span id=\"usstock_TSM\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/TSM.html\" target=\"_blank\">台积电</a></span><span id=\"quote_TSM\"></span>跌0.22%，<span id=\"usstock_PDD\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/PDD.html\" target=\"_blank\">拼多多</a></span><span id=\"quote_PDD\"></span>跌5.40%，<span id=\"usstock_NTES\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/NTES.html\" target=\"_blank\">网易</a></span><span id=\"quote_NTES\"></span>跌1.97%，<span id=\"usstock_BIDU\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/BIDU.html\" target=\"_blank\">百度</a></span><span id=\"quote_BIDU\"></span>跌1.91%，携程跌4.15%，<span id=\"usstock_JD\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/JD.html\" target=\"_blank\">京东</a></span><span id=\"quote_JD\"></span>跌2.77%，<span id=\"usstock_CHT\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/CHT.html\" target=\"_blank\">中华电信</a></span><span id=\"quote_CHT\"></span>跌0.30%，<span id=\"usstock_TME\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/TME.html\" target=\"_blank\">腾讯音乐</a></span><span id=\"quote_TME\"></span>跌0.93%，<span id=\"usstock_FUTU\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/FUTU.html\" target=\"_blank\">富途</a></span><span id=\"quote_FUTU\"></span>控股跌2.14%，<span id=\"usstock_UMC\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/UMC.html\" target=\"_blank\">联电</a></span><span id=\"quote_UMC\"></span>跌2.15%，小鹏汽车跌3.06%，<span id=\"usstock_BEKE\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/BEKE.html\" target=\"_blank\">贝壳</a></span><span id=\"quote_BEKE\"></span>跌3.37%，<span id=\"usstock_LI\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/LI.html\" target=\"_blank\">理想</a></span><span id=\"quote_LI\"></span>汽车跌2.35%，<span id=\"usstock_HTHT\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/HTHT.html\" target=\"_blank\">华住酒店集团</a></span><span id=\"quote_HTHT\"></span>跌2.74%，<span id=\"usstock_BILI\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/BILI.html\" target=\"_blank\">哔哩哔哩</a></span><span id=\"quote_BILI\"></span>跌1.20%，中国新城农村跌1.08%，<span id=\"usstock_NIO\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/NIO.html\" target=\"_blank\">蔚来</a></span><span id=\"quote_NIO\"></span>跌3.09%。</p>\n<p>　　美股周二收跌，道指下跌约400点。<span id=\"usstock_JPM\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/JPM.html\" target=\"_blank\">摩根大通</a></span><span id=\"quote_JPM\"></span>下挫逾4%。围绕央行独立性的担忧依然存在。投资者正努力应对过去几天美国总统特朗普提出的一系列提议引发的市场波动。</p>\n<p>　　道指跌398.21点，跌幅为0.80%，报49191.99点；纳指跌24.03点，跌幅为0.10%，报23709.87点；标普500指数跌13.56点，跌幅为0.19%，报6963.71点。</p>\n<p>　　领涨中概股列表：</p>\n<div class=\"img_wrapper\"><img alt=\"\" data-link=\"\" src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/tech/transform/703/w550h1753/20260114/7ab7-76d5615da1fa7a2bdd2709541e3b566f.png\"/><span class=\"img_descr\"></span></div>\n<p>　　领跌中概股列表：</p>\n<div class=\"img_wrapper\"><img alt=\"\" data-link=\"\" src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/tech/transform/385/w550h3035/20260114/e7c9-f114fb60a9e1bb8c57cede3320d97ee4.png\"/><span class=\"img_descr\"></span></div>\n<p>　　<a data-comos-dataid=\"wpcomos:148309\" href=\"http://finance.sina.cn/app/auto_download_finapp.shtml\" target=\"_blank\">（截图来自新浪财经APP 行情-美股-中概股热门板块）下载新浪财经APP</a></p><!-- news_keyword_pub,usstock,NTES&BIDU&JPM&.IXIC&ASX&TSM&UMC&HTHT&CHT&JD&BABA&BABA&ZTO&BILI&PDD&NIO&TME&FUTU&LI&BEKE -->\n<!-- 正文下iframe -->\n<!-- 正文下iframe -->\n<!-- 总声明-->\n<!-- 总声明-->\n<!-- 文末二维码 start -->\n<!-- 文末二维码 start -->\n\n\n<!-- 文末二维码 start -->\n<!-- 文末二维码 start -->\n<!-- 编辑姓名及工作代码 -->\n\n<!-- 编辑姓名及工作代码-->\n</div>",
            "link": "https://finance.sina.com.cn/stock/usstock/c/2026-01-14/doc-inhhffax6933192.shtml",
            "summary": "1月14日热门中概股多数下跌，纳斯达克中国金龙指数（HXC）收跌1.86%。 上涨股当中（按市值从高到低），阿里巴巴涨0.40%，日月光半导体涨2.38%，中通涨0.14%。",
            "author": "",
